{"tid":1514342,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"鐵路Online!!!未玩過同我入黎!!!","createTime":"2019-08-28T16:53:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T14:58:54.000Z","uid":125469,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"094821d1c7ab1e7fbe8528077bdceb713c4571d2","tid":1514342,"uid":125469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:53:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 最近發現到呢個GAME幾好玩,好真實<br />\n想話開個攻略一齊玩!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">遊戲目的:</span>打經濟牌,減少鐵路公司收入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">攻略黎啦</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實你要做既只有一件事:用<span style=\"color: red;\">最少既資源</span>過閘機<br />\n<br />\n方法一:暴力式<span style=\"color: blue;\">(COST=0)</span><br />\n玩家多既時侯搵人禁住個闊閘機門全部直行直過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方法二:跳閘式/捐山窿式<span style=\"color: blue;\">(COST=0)</span><br />\n缺點係唔係人人跳到同礙眼<br />\n<br />\n方法三:尾隨式<span style=\"color: blue;\">(COST=0)</span><br />\n每班車好多人出閘,等D人出得7788尾隨最後一個,用<span style=\"color: red;\">八達通套</span>出閘<br />\n你冇睇錯係<span style=\"color: red;\">八達通套</span>,闊閘機先work<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方法四:綠卡<span style=\"color: blue;\">(COST=2)</span><br />\n不解釋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">防禦篇</span><br />\n1.留意CCTV/黃精靈<br />\n2.Black block/唔好有咩裝飾明顯野<br />\n3.有冇人係你後面出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">成功率加乘篇</span><br />\n1.大量玩家(玩開online game 都知組隊打怪係易好多)<br />\n2.組隊(壯膽,可以用尾隨式)<br />\n3.太早/太晏(人少)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">黃左篇</span>(酒呀!!!我黃左走唔到架啦!!!一個人死好過全部人死呀!!!)<br />\n1.轉玩跑online<br />\n2.兇佢/作勢郁佢<span style=\"color: red;\">(千其唔好黎真)</span>,再轉玩跑online<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港,時代革命,天佑吾城</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屌那媽,頂硬上</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a9b86d96a3dfb905328695b744bbb03b8a4b05","tid":1514342,"uid":125469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"呂麗呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c887323bf86ee362f81e9bc604bbcf607df8a0","tid":1514342,"uid":148082,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NZN2j21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNZN2j21.jpg&h=ca78fec3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6zfjngn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6zfjngn.jpg&h=c158cc0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"864bd95b21d96ca5000ca231507a0cd68f85fcb1","tid":1514342,"uid":125469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:22:47.000Z","msg":"多謝樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"3dc0bcca465b670cc0bfb67c793fd57df5240f1b","tid":1514342,"uid":125469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:51:08.000Z","msg":"推,比D意見呀"},{"pid":"e336a258acf92cbbd68d2b788777ec724fadcf8a","tid":1514342,"uid":125469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:03:52.000Z","msg":"睇完幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892846316ba4a67dbfb439b1315ae0e54584b443","tid":1514342,"uid":125469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:22:22.000Z","msg":"女仔成日驚跳唔過又唔入黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e5f5a3b2c34d07f903204ab003f70785cf4cd4","tid":1514342,"uid":149779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T23:56:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8aa805cff0b14f22aefd291fb46c67d24e60243e","tid":1514342,"uid":308152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"